WEBVTT

00:08:56.229 --> 00:09:03.226
because her husband was sickly,
and he would go out --

00:09:03.250 --> 00:09:07.313
and people from Chicago
and all the places,

00:09:07.337 --> 00:09:11.051
you would call his job a numbers runner.

00:09:11.931 --> 00:09:15.097
But in New Orleans,
we are very sophisticated --

00:09:15.121 --> 00:09:16.121
(Laughter)

00:09:16.145 --> 00:09:17.852
so it wasn't a numbers runner,

00:09:17.876 --> 00:09:19.932
it was a lottery vendor.

00:09:19.956 --> 00:09:21.630
(Laughter)

00:09:21.654 --> 00:09:23.663
So you see, we put class to that.

00:09:23.687 --> 00:09:24.933
But that's how he did it.

00:09:24.957 --> 00:09:29.999
And he couldn't go from house to house
to get his clients and all that,